subject: Freestyle Skiing
Olympic Games (2010)
Skiing
lead_paragraph: As Jennifer Heil, a Canadian, finished second behind the American skier Hannah Kearney, Canada failed to pry loose the monkey clinging to the back of its Olympic fortunes.
